                  frame.style.width = '100vw';

                    frame.style.visibility = 'visible';

                    frame.style.visibility = 'hidden';

<h2 id="overview" class="sl-link-heading sl-text-4xl sl-leading-tight sl-font-prose sl-font-bold sl-text-heading"><a href="#overview" class="sl-link sl-link-heading__link sl-inline-flex sl-items-center sl-text-current"><div>Overview</div><div class="sl-link-heading__icon sl-text-base sl-ml-4 sl-text-muted"><i role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="sl-icon fal fa-link"></i></div></a></h2>
<p><a href="https://sleekflow.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">SleekFlow</a> offers APIs that empower you to enhance your existing platforms or applications through custom integration with SleekFlow's platform, messaging capabilities, and features.
Unlock the power of SleekFlow's omni-channel social commerce platform, enabling you to sell, promote, and improve customer support through messaging channels.</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="explore-sleekflow-api" class="sl-link-heading sl-text-4xl sl-leading-tight sl-font-prose sl-font-bold sl-text-heading"><a href="#explore-sleekflow-api" class="sl-link sl-link-heading__link sl-inline-flex sl-items-center sl-text-current"><div>Explore SleekFlow API</div><div class="sl-link-heading__icon sl-text-base sl-ml-4 sl-text-muted"><i role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="sl-icon fal fa-link"></i></div></a></h2>
<h3 id="sleekflow-platform-api" class="sl-link-heading sl-text-2xl sl-leading-snug sl-font-prose sl-font-semibold sl-text-heading"><a href="#sleekflow-platform-api" class="sl-link sl-link-heading__link sl-inline-flex sl-items-center sl-text-current"><div><a href="/docs/platform-api">SleekFlow Platform API</a></div><div class="sl-link-heading__icon sl-text-base sl-ml-4 sl-text-muted"><i role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="sl-icon fal fa-link"></i></div></a></h3>
<p>Get started with our <a href="/docs/platform-api">SleekFlow Platform API</a> to create custom integration with SleekFlow's messaging capabilities and features!</p>
